high_descs: Go to the toilet to the left.
Pick up the bottle farthest to the left.
Go to the tub near the toilet.
Place the bottle on the tub's counter.
Return to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle that is farthest right.
Go to the tub near the toilet.
Place the bottle to the right of the bottle on the counter.
Turn and go to the toilet.
Pick up a soap dispenser on the toilet.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Put the soap dispenser on the counter next to the bathtub.
Turn and go to the toilet.
Pick up a soap dispenser on the toilet.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Put the soap dispenser on the counter next to the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Move two soap dispensers from the toilet to the counter by the bathtub.

high_descs: Take a step forward and turn left towards the wall and then turn left to face the toilet basin.
Pick up the lotion bottle next to the purple spray bottle.
Take a step to the left and face the bath tub.
Place the lotion bottle on the bath tub counter.
Take a step to the right to face the toilet basin.
Pick up the outside lotion bottle.
Take a step to the left to face the bath tub counter.
Place the lotion bottle beside the other bottle on the bath tub counter.
anns.task_desc: Transfer two lotion bottles from the toilet basin to the bath tub counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left so you are on the right side of the toilet, looking towards it
Pick up a bottle off of the toilet
Move to your left so you are facing the bath tub
Place the bottle on the side of the bath tub
Go back to where you were standing previously
Pick up another bottle off of the toilet
Return to your previous position facing the bath tub
Place the second bottle on the side of the bath tub
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles next to the bath tub

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the ride side of the toilet.
Pick up the lotion bottle closest to the purple spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Take one step left and face the counter next to the tub.
Place the lotion bottle on the counter next to the tub.
Take one step to the right and then face the toilet.
Pick up the lotion bottle farthest from the purple spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Take one step left and then face the counter next to the tub.
Place the lotion bottle to the right of the other bottle on the counter next to the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles of lotion on the counter to the right of the tub.
